info.description: SMIB system with one load and GENROE model

eXST1.imLeadLag.TF.x[1].comment: State of transfer function from controller canonical form

constantLoad.S_i.im.comment: Imaginary part of complex power (reactive power)

constantLoad.S_i.re.comment: Real part of complex power (active power)

constantLoad.S_p.im.comment: Imaginary part of complex power (reactive power)

constantLoad.S_p.re.comment: Real part of complex power (active power)

constantLoad.S_y.im.comment: Imaginary part of complex power (reactive power)

constantLoad.S_y.re.comment: Real part of complex power (active power)

eXST1.K_C.comment: Rectifier loading factor proportional to commutating reactance

eXST1.K_a.k.comment: Gain value multiplied with input signal

eXST1.imDerivativeLag.T.comment: Time constants (T>0 required; T=0 is ideal derivative block)

eXST1.imDerivativeLag.x_start.comment: Initial or guess value of state

eXST1.imLeadLag.TF.a[1].comment: Denominator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 5*s+6 is specified as {5,6})

eXST1.imLeadLag.TF.a[2].comment: Denominator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 5*s+6 is specified as {5,6})

eXST1.imLeadLag.TF.b[1].comment: Numerator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 2*s+3 is specified as {2,3})

eXST1.imLeadLag.TF.b[2].comment: Numerator coefficients of transfer function (e.g., 2*s+3 is specified as {2,3})

eXST1.imLeadLag.TF.x_start[1].comment: Initial or guess values of states

eXST1.imLeadLag.TF.y_start.comment: Initial value of output (derivatives of y are zero up to nx-1-th derivative)

gENCLS.CoB.comment: Change from system to machine base

gENROE.PMECH0.comment: Initial value of machine electrical power (pu, machine base)

gENROE.PSIppd0.comment: d-axis component of the sub-transient flux linkage

gENROE.PSIppq0.comment: q-axis component of the sub-transient flux linkage

gENROE.dsat.comment: To include saturation of during initialization

gENROE.ii0.comment: Imaginary component of initial armature current (pu, system base)

gENROE.ir0.comment: Real component of initial armature current (pu, system base)

gENROE.p0.comment: Initial active power generation (pu, machine base)

gENROE.q0.comment: Initial reactive power generation (pu, machine base)

gENROE.vi0.comment: Imaginary component of initial terminal voltage

gENROE.vr0.comment: Real component of initial terminal voltage

eXST1.imLeadLag.TF.initType.comment: Type of initialization (1: no init, 2: steady state, 3: initial state, 4: initial output)

eXST1.imLeadLag.TF.na.comment: Size of Denominator of transfer function.

eXST1.imLeadLag.TF.nb.comment: Size of Numerator of transfer function.

eXST1.limiter.limitsAtInit.comment: Has no longer an effect and is only kept for backwards compatibility (the implementation uses now the homotopy operator)

eXST1.limiter.strict.comment: = true, if strict limits with noEvent(..)
